      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring leather that remains supple and a dash completely free of wear or sun damage. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by authorized dealers. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seats, functions exactly as intended, offering a driving experience identical to a brand-new car.",
