    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and refined aesthetics. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical integrity, this unit features a sophisticated interior and a powertrain engineered for longevity. It represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber automotive asset. Experience the fusion of luxury and dependability in a vehicle that stands as a testament to diligent ownership.",
      "price": 35400.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
