      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a fantastic car that still feels fresh and fun on the road. Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable daily driver without breaking the bank. Come take it for a spin, I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home!",
      "price": 29500.0,
