    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving mill features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced with plates. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, currently benefitting from upgraded poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in. While the exterior shows honest wear, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent compression across all cylinders. A true driver\u2019s specification for the purist.",
